Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,琉...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,琉·璃昂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,琉...好难念哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,决定了 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天开始我就叫你璃昂吧
